OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,362,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1777036266
OL,3,CMan who killed peacemaker in pub fight
OL,4,Cjailed
OL,6,FMr Fox was one of several who stepped
OL,7,Fin, before Price threw a punch at him,
OL,8,Fcausing him to fall back and hit his
OL,9,Fhead on the concrete ground.
OL,11,FHe was taken to hospital and placed on
OL,12,Flife support, but did not regain
OL,13,Fconsciousness and died two days later.
OL,15,FDespite initially claiming he acted in
OL,16,Fself-defence, Price pled guilty to
OL,17,Fmanslaughter and assault occasioning
OL,18,Factual bodily harm and was jailed for
OL,19,Ffive years and 11 months at Nottingham
OL,20,FCrown Court on Friday.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/7
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,362,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1777036266
OL,3,CMan who killed peacemaker in pub fight
OL,4,Cjailed
OL,6,FWitnesses described Price as "looking
OL,7,Ffor a fight" on the night of the
OL,8,Fincident, which was caught on CCTV.
OL,10,FMr Fox, a father and qualified
OL,11,Felectrician who was engaged to be
OL,12,Fmarried, was described as a "young,
OL,13,Fhealthy person and would not cause any
OL,14,Ftrouble to anyone".
OL,16,FIn a victim impact statement, his
OL,17,Ffiancee told the court: "Harley is
OL,18,Freferred to as 'the victim' in this
OL,19,Fcase, but he was so much more than
OL,20,Fthat.
OL,26,@yD@YOU
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/7
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
