OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,362,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1777036266
OL,3,CMan who killed peacemaker in pub fight
OL,4,Cjailed
OL,6,F"Harley was an honest, funny, and
OL,7,Floving man. He was hard-working,
OL,8,Fthoughtful, and always put others
OL,9,Fbefore himself. He made sure our
OL,10,Fdaughter and I were safe, cared for,
OL,11,Fand happy. We had a loving home,
OL,12,Fshared holidays, laughter, and plans
OL,13,Ffor the future. All of this was ripped
OL,14,Faway in an instant by Dilon Price."
OL,26,@vD@cO]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/7
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
