OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,362,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1777036266
OL,3,CMan who killed peacemaker in pub fight
OL,4,Cjailed
OL,6,FMr Fox's mother told the court:
OL,7,F"Harley should be alive, he should be
OL,8,Fable to live his life, see his family
OL,9,Fgrow, be able to walk his daughter
OL,10,Fdown the aisle for her wedding and
OL,11,Fexperience the love and pride of
OL,12,Fbecoming a grandad.
OL,14,F"I am so proud of the man my son
OL,15,FHarley became. He was clever, funny,
OL,16,Fkind, and friendly and he had the
OL,17,Fbiggest heart. He would help anyone
OL,18,Fand would always be loyal and
OL,19,Fprotective to those in need.
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@AOU
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/7
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,362,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1777036266
OL,3,CMan who killed peacemaker in pub fight
OL,4,Cjailed
OL,6,F"Harley was like the fourth emergency
OL,7,Fservice in our family. We all knew if
OL,8,Fthere was ever a problem such as a car
OL,9,Fissue or house repairs, or even just
OL,10,Fdealing with a moth, then Harley would
OL,11,Fbe there to help.
OL,13,F"This has all been taken away because
OL,14,Fof one man's stupid and aggressive
OL,15,Factions."
OL,26,@uD@AOUwD@IO]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G6/7
