PN,36107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1777036266
OL,3,CMan who killed peacemaker in pub fight
OL,4,Cjailed
OL,6,FDet Insp Matt Scott, of
OL,7,FNottinghamshire Police added: "A life
OL,8,Fhas been cut short following what
OL,9,Fshould have been an enjoyable evening
OL,10,Fat the pub. The behaviour displayed by
OL,11,FDilon Price was totally unacceptable
OL,12,Fand his actions have led to untold
OL,13,Fmisery for Harvey's family and
OL,14,Ffriends."
